Mid-term 4문제 (아캠에 기출 올라가 있음)
5월 5일까지임.

Lambda expression
Functional programming language의 근간.
Input, output, body로 이루어짐.

While applying lambda calculation, it is quite inefficient. So the five rules were introduced.
(Formal to informal representation (1/3) slide)
Calculating lambda expression (informal) ->1 problem.

Free variables.
Names of variables are quite immaterial.
Scoping rule.

Why lambda expression? Very compact.

Substitution
V=X and X is not free=> x cannot change anything.

β-reduction
Eliminate as many abstraction as possible.
3번처럼 헷갈리는 케이스들 나올 확률 높음.
